<dl id="n52083d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n52" href="#n52083d">N52 (VI.B.42)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n52all.htm#n52083d"> 83(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> truth with some / stretchers</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">That book was made by Mr. Mark Twain, and he told the truth, mainly &hellip; <font color="green">[it]</font> is mostly <mark>a true book; with some stretchers</mark>, as I said before. <small> Mark Twain, <a name="MTHF1" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#MTHF1"><cite title="source">Huckleberry Finn</cite></a> (ed. unknown) I</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
